entries.femaleVariant: Let's play a game. I give you a little boo-boo – you start crying, I start laughing.
First I'm going to chop you up, then I'll sell you like oh-so-many spare parts.
Time's up! Finito! Your gonk, pathetic life is in my hands now.
I'm gonna end you. That's it – there's no going back, understand?
